I'm guilty of something I didn't do.

203
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:07,545
Well, that's your decision.

204
00:11:08,542 --> 00:11:11,314
But I recommend you take the deal.

205
00:11:20,463 --> 00:11:22,153
We left Justin's place.

206
